title: The Beatles - Extracts From The Album A Hard Day's Night EP [320
description:
Extracts from the Album A Hard Day's Night is The Beatles seventh official EP, released on 6 November 1964. This EP contains four tracks from the album, but not featured in the film. Its catalogue number is Parlophone GEP 8924. It was also released in France.
